<quantity id="4CDE21EF7152B005FBFE50A8FB7011DD" box="[1083,1185,158,185]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="0.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="109" unit="m" value="250.0" valueMax="500.0" valueMin="0.0">
